title: A Massive Roblox Lawsuit is Happening Right Now...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a lawsuit regarding Roblox and how they refuse to clean up their platform for their younger fanbase. While the case appears weak it's evident that Roblox has a serious problem with how they let illegitimate sites interact with their network. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
